></blockquote><br />\n我信呀，我依家合埋眼都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc14698243eb7298d88317b0a976c73a09b6bfa0","tid":188371,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眼分泌俾光射出嚟掛</blockquote><br />\n但全黑環境都見到"},{"pid":"d82af8b467b4f1544515ac2173524ab40f2c8e69","tid":188371,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前睇過篇嘢話係自己啲細胞嚟</blockquote><br />\n是咪真呀，游黎游去嫁喎"},{"pid":"e966863a24a907dd605637be90c0ca147626e087","tid":188371,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時仲有d 紅綠點點，但冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有呢個情況，都係冇人信<br />\n係咪好似水晶球入邊既閃粉咁呢，多數出現幾秒至十秒就唔見左"},{"pid":"7ca8a0ea5e2fc12d34522c311238d698edf43ae2","tid":188371,"uid":99459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前睇過篇嘢話係自己啲細胞嚟</blockquote><br />\n是咪真呀，游黎游去嫁喎</blockquote><br />\n係白血球"},{"pid":"565249cc70e95dea9afac44693881a23446c3bb3","tid":188371,"uid":35233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前睇過篇嘢話係自己啲細胞嚟</blockquote><br />\n是咪真呀，游黎游去嫁喎</blockquote><br />\n真係幾似細胞"},{"pid":"e4f9fe109c0096125083212a6359d170e6a2adc9","tid":188371,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>麥皮蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似似地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有麥皮蟲夜晚走咗入你隻眼生蛋 你今次仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9145ffe8dd089627a00cdf32ac0250bb0e8846da","tid":188371,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"係咪絕症？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a22d2c9795b17000a2724e360b4d47e2ea903f4","tid":188371,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飛蚊</blockquote><br />\n我平時見開啲蚊唔係咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真心定假膠呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你見開啲蚊一條條？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngoogle飛蚊症"},{"pid":"781622578cd9b340887796be22ef9504675c848f","tid":188371,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時仲有d 紅綠點點，但冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有呢個情況，都係冇人信<br />\n係咪好似水晶球入邊既閃粉咁呢，多數出現幾秒至十秒就唔見左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己估 果下其實係d血流唔夠入隻眼，所以唔關光唔光事<br />\n<br />\n至於蟲蟲，我關頭以為係丫米巴變形蟲 但我望左好耐都見唔到佢郁      我有估過係細胞，但又唔認為會單靠眼睇到"},{"pid":"e671b5a9a10b9373327338ef12137ba1a6872013","tid":188371,"uid":23414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"記得小學考試等收卷 就喺睇啲蟲蟲解悶"},{"pid":"5d8949ac7d8cdcfd03ef795b0b508c5ec3c87e7b","tid":188371,"uid":97634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:05:55.000Z","msg":"有時坐底起身都會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d308afc6c7628a1c051456505dc3bf794031e0","tid":188371,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"好黑既宇宙"},{"pid":"078f1eae0a272759e0eee9d08c0a7542437ff265","tid":188371,"uid":60779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時仲有d 紅綠點點，但冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢d係電子產品輻射留影<br />\n樓主個d係自己眼入邊d細胞黎<br />\n詳情請google"},{"pid":"8ee0e851fe59b3f6de8fcc2dfd0895300f174dad","tid":188371,"uid":62064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:20:40.000Z","msg":"以前就係因為飛蚊症煩左一輪 依家已經習慣左<br />\n同埋有飛蚊症既同時我都有見到一舊寧寧社社似係cell既物體"},{"pid":"745552bff4e1c56d309122f6846dedc5594d9bf6","tid":188371,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"由細到大都覺得好奇怪 以為有眼疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後大左忙左就冇留意了<br />\n樓主講起又想知係咩原因"},{"pid":"1315813fb2fda293e1b0d9bcadcfb940607cadf9","tid":188371,"uid":53739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認同上邊話細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45f843492f8e7f5e1d98a6a4973be2fbbab3124","tid":188371,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"飛雞症"},{"pid":"6de547ea94f65b9343ce8650ff72d482358b7946","tid":188371,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"白血球"},{"pid":"14bf179b93a2b107e30e783e4eb98a592b606dc7","tid":188371,"uid":71919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"1.漂浮物的學名<br />\n<br />\n原來在眼來游來游去的微生物是有學名的，他們的學名是Muscae Volitantes，拉丁語是「飛蠅」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n雖然它的學名是「飛蠅」，但其實它們並不是昆蟲，而是我們體內的物質。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 漂浮物是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n它們在我們看東西的時候游來游去，以至很多人都誤會眼來的漂浮物是有生命的。<br />\n<br />\n它們可能是組織丶紅血球或蛋白質塊。因為它們在眼內的玻璃體漂浮，所以會跟著眼球的移動方向一起移動。"},{"pid":"00b4714c72fb8cd273e74cc133d3af5c6013a787","tid":188371,"uid":94441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F927419%2F%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%A7%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E8%9F%B2%E8%9F%B2%E3%80%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=41ff8433\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？</a>"},{"pid":"194481e5e62fadd25a152ae971dbbe3e28cedad3","tid":188371,"uid":36745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得小學考試等收卷 就喺睇啲蟲蟲解悶</blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大大力闔埋對眼必啲蟲蟲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1fe8e15f360935ff2c4ef96e4e7579bfbb32ab","tid":188371,"uid":61557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲應該係普通飛蚊黎 你驚既話去驗下眼<br />\n上面有人話係丫米巴變形蟲 如果係既話你應該一早痛到去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71e877d34637f6409d45d3312c00b5556e7abb7","tid":188371,"uid":32623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"講細胞果d係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5ca93d72697ad050a574afb005861886ab06c5","tid":188371,"uid":87380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"好似係白血球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab024ac40a25a0ae92591c659e6ccdde6aa13955","tid":188371,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:38:00.000Z","msg":"視網膜上既細胞"},{"pid":"e443b451d0678b284dc588dddf4120208719393a","tid":188371,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:40:40.000Z","msg":"我都有<br />\n係咪由左至右咁飛，一點點（似正方形多）咁？<br />\n又好似紅、又好似藍、又好似綠，但講唔出係乜色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50014870d34fddc19e38b29663c756528e0f994","tid":188371,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.漂浮物的學名<br />\n<br />\n原來在眼來游來游去的微生物是有學名的，他們的學名是Muscae Volitantes，拉丁語是「飛蠅」的意思。<br />\n<br />\n雖然它的學名是「飛蠅」，但其實它們並不是昆蟲，而是我們體內的物質。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 漂浮物是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n它們在我們看東西的時候游來游去，以至很多人都誤會眼來的漂浮物是有生命的。<br />\n<br />\n它們可能是組織丶紅血球或蛋白質塊。因為它們在眼內的玻璃體漂浮，所以會跟著眼球的移動方向一起移動。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係2，2係黑色"},{"pid":"fa706a262b2c3d59145fb06abe03c2e0219924ba","tid":188371,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F927419%2F%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%A7%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E8%9F%B2%E8%9F%B2%E3%80%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=41ff8433\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呢種，呢種係黑色，對眼郁，啲黑蟲先郁，要強光地方先明顯。<br />\n<br />\nop講果種應該係有顏色一點點咁，就算對眼唔郁，啲點點都一直無限和同一方向loop，黑房都睇到。"},{"pid":"a73a9b3b2ca6fe9462cf407aa01002c6d106e834","tid":188371,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F927419%2F%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%A7%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E8%9F%B2%E8%9F%B2%E3%80%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=41ff8433\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呢種，呢種係黑色，對眼郁，啲黑蟲先郁，要強光地方先明顯。<br />\n<br />\nop講果種應該係有顏色一點點咁，就算對眼唔郁，啲點點都一直無限和同一方向loop，黑房都睇到。</blockquote><br />\n我兩樣都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8825a05df6b4db61e87c0d330fea075695b3adfa","tid":188371,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F927419%2F%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%A7%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E8%9F%B2%E8%9F%B2%E3%80%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%EF%BC%9F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=41ff8433\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/927419/眼內的「蟲蟲」到底是甚麼？</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呢種，呢種係黑色，對眼郁，啲黑蟲先郁，要強光地方先明顯。<br />\n<br />\nop講果種應該係有顏色一點點咁，就算對眼唔郁，啲點點都一直無限和同一方向loop，黑房都睇到。</blockquote><br />\n我兩樣都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係，所以先知係兩樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b774e18cf1f6a2dfccd610f9dbdef5d2dbed60","tid":188371,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前睇過篇嘢話係自己啲細胞嚟</blockquote><br />\n是咪真呀，游黎游去嫁喎</blockquote><br />\n飛蚊症<br />\n我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a544fd70d9fc7b62e792a03d2f1ff1da87775b","tid":188371,"uid":84336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T18:33:12.000Z","msg":"細細個試過有 都係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後去咗睇眼科，驗完眼醫生話正常冇野，個d係眼嘅細胞etc. （好似樓上幾位巴打講咁）<br />\n如果你都係好驚就驗下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac1c9782dd43c75bf28fce6dc91ef614941a34d","tid":188371,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T19:12:35.000Z","msg":"屌我小學已經留意到呢樣野, 同醫生講我睇到細胞又唔信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我宜家都唔信真係細胞wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk